1.00	Kanoa_Leahey	Kanoa Leahey	James Kanoa Leahey, known as Kanoa Leahey, is the Sports Director for KHON-TV, the Honolulu Fox affiliate. In addition to broadcasting the Monday-Friday sportscasts, he is also a Play by Play Announcer for high school sports on Oceanic Cable, as well as co-host of Leahey &amp; Leahey, a weekly talk show featured on PBS Hawaii, and host of a radio show on AM 1500-Honolulu, a sports news affiliate with his father Jim (Leahey &amp; Leahey Live).	
